f,g
\mathbb R^{2n}
 f\star g = \exp\left(-\omega^{ij} \frac{\partial}{\partial y^i} \frac{\partial}{\partial z^j}\right) f(y)g(z) \vert_{z=y}. 
\omega^{ij}
\mathbb R^{2n}
\def\dd#1{\tfrac{\partial}{\partial #1}}
\dd{x}\Big(f(x,y)|_{x=y}\Big) = \Bigg(\Big(\dd x+\dd y\Big)f(x,y)\Bigg)\Bigg|_{x=y}
E(\dd{y}, \dd{z})=\exp(-\omega^{i,j}\dd{y^i}\dd{z^j})
 (f\star g)(x)=\Big(E(\dd{x},\dd{y})\cdot\big(f(x)g(y)\big)\Big)\Big|_{x=y}
